{"word":"ἀποσκλῆναι","slug":"ἀποσκλῆναι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀποσκλῆναι</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>as if from *<el>ἀπόσκλημι</el> (<a href='S:confer, compare'>cf.</a> <a href='S:σκέλλω'><el>σκέλλω</el></a>),\n<p/><i>to be dried up, to wither</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>; so <a href='S:perfect tense'>perf.</a> <el>ἀπέσκληκα</el> <b><a href='S:Lucian'>Luc.</a></b>; <a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>ἀποσκλήσω</el> <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/>"}]}